# Documentation Index

This directory stores the shared documentation system for {{project_name}}.

## Main Documents

- `code-style-guide.md`: code and writing conventions
- `task-delivery-guide.md`: what each task should document
- `task-execution-template.md`: execution order and final checks
- `repo-workflow-guide.md`: branch, commit, and Jira workflow rules
- `doc-templates.md`: reusable document templates
- `domain-overview.md`: domain summary
- `architecture.md`: repository and system shape
- `roadmap.md`: staged direction
- `constraints.md`: explicit boundaries and non-goals
- `legacy-reshape-guide.md`: how to document and reshape an existing repository
- `legacy-structure-inventory.md`: current-state structure inventory for a legacy repository
- `{{release_version}}/features/`: versioned feature notes and checklists

## Rule

Project-specific documents should either fit this system or justify why they need a new place.
